text: Zeta Emilianidou (; 2 September 1954 â€“ 6 June 2022) was a Cypriot lawyer and politician. She was the Minister of Labour and Social Security of Cyprus from 4 April 2013 until her death on 6 June 2022. Emilianidou was born Nicosia, Cyprus. Emilianidou died on 6 June 2022 in Athens, Greece from problems caused by a ruptured brain aneurysm, aged 67. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Cypriot politicians Category:Cypriot lawyers Category:Deaths from intracranial aneurysm
